Package: ChIASim
Type: Package
Title: ChIASim
Version: 1.0
Author: Shuyuan Lou (The Ohio State University, USA), Shili Lin (The Ohio State University, USA)
Maintainer: Shuyuan Lou <lou.59@osu.edu>
Description: ChIASim is a realistic simulation algorithm that is designed to generate simulated ChIA-PET or Hi-ChIP data, by mimicking major steps of ChIA-PET experiment. 
